# 三、數值函數 (Numeric)

| 函數         | 說明     | 示例                            |
| ---------- | ------ | ----------------------------- |
| ABS()      | 絕對值    | `SELECT ABS(-10);`            |
| ROUND()    | 四捨五入   | `SELECT ROUND(3.14159,2);`    |
| CEIL()     | 向上取整   | `SELECT CEIL(3.2);`           |
| FLOOR()    | 向下取整   | `SELECT FLOOR(3.8);`          |
| MOD()      | 取餘數    | `SELECT MOD(10,3);`           |
| RAND()     | 隨機數    | `SELECT RAND();`              |
| POWER()    | 次方     | `SELECT POWER(2,3);`          |
| SQRT()     | 平方根    | `SELECT SQRT(16);`            |
| SIGN()     | 正負值    | `SELECT SIGN(-5);`            |
| PI()       | 圓周率    | `SELECT PI();`                |
| EXP()      | 指數     | `SELECT EXP(2);`              |
| LOG()      | 對數     | `SELECT LOG(10);`             |
| LOG10()    | 10為底對數 | `SELECT LOG10(100);`          |
| GREATEST() | 最大值    | `SELECT GREATEST(3,7,5);`     |
| LEAST()    | 最小值    | `SELECT LEAST(3,7,5);`        |
| TRUNCATE() | 截斷小數   | `SELECT TRUNCATE(3.14159,2);` |
| FORMAT()   | 格式化數字  | `SELECT FORMAT(1234.567,2);`  |
| CONV()     | 進制轉換   | `SELECT CONV(10,10,2);`       |
| CRC32()    | CRC校驗  | `SELECT CRC32('hello');`      |

---

# 四、聚合函數 (Aggregate)

| 函數             | 說明    | 示例                                      |
| -------------- | ----- | --------------------------------------- |
| COUNT()        | 計數    | `SELECT COUNT(*) FROM users;`           |
| SUM()          | 求和    | `SELECT SUM(price) FROM orders;`        |
| AVG()          | 平均值   | `SELECT AVG(score) FROM exam;`          |
| MAX()          | 最大值   | `SELECT MAX(price) FROM products;`      |
| MIN()          | 最小值   | `SELECT MIN(price) FROM products;`      |
| GROUP_CONCAT() | 字符串聚合 | `SELECT GROUP_CONCAT(name) FROM users;` |
| VARIANCE()     | 方差    | `SELECT VARIANCE(score) FROM exam;`     |
| STDDEV()       | 標準差   | `SELECT STDDEV(score) FROM exam;`       |
| BIT_AND()      | 位與    | `SELECT BIT_AND(flag) FROM table1;`     |
| BIT_OR()       | 位或    | `SELECT BIT_OR(flag) FROM table1;`      |

---

# 五、流程控制函數 (Control Flow)

| 函數         | 說明       | 示例                                    |
| ---------- | -------- | ------------------------------------- |
| IF()       | 條件判斷     | `SELECT IF(score>60,'PASS','FAIL');`  |
| IFNULL()   | NULL處理   | `SELECT IFNULL(phone,'N/A');`         |
| NULLIF()   | 相等返回NULL | `SELECT NULLIF(1,1);`                 |
| CASE       | 條件分支     | `CASE WHEN score>60 THEN 'PASS' END`  |
| COALESCE() | 第一個非NULL | `SELECT COALESCE(NULL,NULL,'Hello');` |
| ISNULL()   | 判斷NULL   | `SELECT ISNULL(NULL);`                |
| FIELD()    | 返回索引     | `SELECT FIELD('b','a','b','c');`      |
| ELT()      | 返回列表值    | `SELECT ELT(2,'a','b','c');`          |

